data.title: Troy Nash greeting Prince Ghazi of Jordan.
data.meta_description: Prince Ghazi bin Muhammad of Jordan (born October 15, 1966 in Amman, Jordan) is a Jordanian prince. He is the son of Prince Muhammad bin Talal of Jordan and his first wife Firyal Irshaid. He is the grandson of the late King Talal I of Jordan. He is married to H.R.H. Princess Areej Ghazi (née Areej Omar Zawawi, of Oman).
